title: Deputy Sheriff sees strange footprints above Strawberry
observed: The Deputy Sheriff from Pinecrest reported hundreds of 15 inch tracks with a 5 foot stride in Leland Meadow, a popluar recreation area.  No casts were made, but news of the tracks made the local paper, the Union Democrat.
location_details: Take Highway 108 to Strawberry, California. The location is about 2 miles northwest of Strawberry in Leland Meadow.
